\id 2TI - Uare
\h 2Timoteo
\toc3 2Tim
\toc2 2Timoteo
\toc1 Timoteo veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Aheuḡa
\mt1 2Timoteo
\mt2 Timoteo veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Aheuḡa
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa
\ip Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Pauloꞌa Roma zamaḡano ḡuꞌa neḡano Timoteo veize mirihiro. Timoteoꞌe Paulo teite harame ragaviro zu Paulo dananiro. Timoteoꞌe Efeso ekalesia ibitozinu ebu Pauloꞌa ibite ani veize soꞌa ꞌahoga tuḡuriro. Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Timoteo veize mirihiroteꞌe soꞌaḡa aheuḡa. Pauloꞌa ane rune madaḡaꞌe hanitiroteꞌe ederadu ane ubuga teigiroteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa iziga, Timoteo mazao ḡonagano iraduguniro. Aniꞌe Timoteoꞌa Keriso ḡoere huga ekalesia ꞌaune ihozifine ḡoreniro. Aduga zamaḡano Keriso mazao fieꞌenaꞌa, zamaḡa obone giganoga veize zu ḡoere huga oboneꞌenaꞌa, edau gigaranoga veize inaraniro. Ebu Timoteoꞌe Efeso ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa radu faine gauiteꞌe moneo iraduguniro.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Eḡe, Pauloꞌa soꞌa ꞌadi miriheꞌohe. Eꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa uratadu Keriso Iesu apostolo vazeḡano reiro. Badiꞌaꞌa Keriso Iesu uꞌano vaze ḡaboziꞌuma rae ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa eḡeꞌa haramifine eḡe ohotiro.
\v 2 Soꞌa ꞌadiꞌe eḡe zamarone ubude Timoteo veize miriheꞌohe.
\p Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama zu emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Keriso Iesuꞌa ḡae mazao manoḡa, vetuḡa zu zama roḡeḡa ḡaneꞌenoꞌi.
\s1 Badiꞌa mazao Manoḡa Tauḡi reiro zu Timoteo Inaraniro
\p 
\v 3 Eḡe vouḡa teige, e zamarone duduḡano zu deheḡano Badiꞌa veize gaueꞌohe. Ebu e ohere zu madai kurauꞌetene, iḡaiḡa ḡa zamareꞌenaꞌa Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi raꞌohe.
\v 4 E ḡaꞌa ibite niaroteꞌe zamareꞌenaꞌa ḡiaꞌihi raꞌohe, mazaḡa e ḡa horoꞌine matuꞌe rudaꞌuma.
\v 5 E ḡaeꞌa zamaḡo niduꞌa hina Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe bare zamareꞌohe. Aḡiḡu roḡaeḡa Loisi zu viꞌu Eunikeꞌa ibite firo, ebu ḡae zuni zeḡe hegotadu izidi hube hune Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe e edere huneꞌohe.
\v 6 Eꞌe uꞌano, ḡa ꞌahi bare zamaroga veize ḡaꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa ḡae rana ꞌevorehe tiroteꞌe madaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa ḡaniroteꞌe ḡahunoneḡa ago daunoꞌi ebu eꞌe hina ꞌaune inare gauoꞌi.
\v 7 Badiꞌaꞌa rifiroteꞌe Vigaꞌe mene riho zamaroneḡa, rehano ane gigiꞌa, vaze zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe, ebu emeꞌa bare haḡai sauꞌa hezahohauꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa.
\p 
\v 8 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡaꞌa emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro moneo rae fureranoga ago mazagaroꞌoꞌi, ebu ani uꞌano e ḡuꞌa neḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe moneo ago mazagaroꞌoꞌi. Rehano Badiꞌa inaraḡa hina Iesu hari manoḡa haramifine, ḡae zuni eḡe teite aduga moꞌi.
\v 9 Badiꞌaꞌa eme ḡabofiro zu emeꞌa zaḡozaḡe radifine hufiro. Aniꞌa ꞌouge haḡairotaꞌaꞌe mene emeḡeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa uꞌano, rehano ane urao emeḡe mazao manoḡa fureniro. Manoḡa aꞌe ꞌizema mada ḡadaheḡano Keriso Iesu mazaonoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa rifiro.
\v 10 Ebu emeḡe ḡabofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Keriso Iesuꞌa rahao fureranadu manoḡa eꞌeꞌa fureraro. Kerisoꞌa rune inaraḡa ruiniro, zu ane hari manoḡa hina mene ruhuratiteꞌe ḡaboneḡa tuḡutuḡu deheru ihofiro.
\v 11 E hari manoḡa ꞌahi haramifine, Iesuꞌa eꞌe haramo vazeḡano zu apostolo vazeḡano zu ihore vazeḡano ohohiro.
\v 12 Eꞌe uꞌano, e izidi ꞌahige aduga hideꞌohe, rehano e mene mazagaroheꞌohe. Mazaḡa e edeḡa hune, eḡeꞌa mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iniu, zu eꞌa ḡabonehe haroteꞌe uꞌano\f + \fr 1:12 \fqa aniꞌa inirotaꞌaꞌe \f* aniꞌa ḡabonehe faine taufiꞌuma, onamo mada ḡonaga.
\p 
\v 13 Ḡa eḡe mazaonoꞌo ihore huga igiro. Ihore aꞌe ḡa Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu ani mazao fieꞌenaꞌa zu vaze zamare borofeꞌenaꞌa, hegote huniteꞌe ihoreḡa rae zamaroꞌi.
\v 14 Emeḡe teite tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ḡa danaꞌeꞌe ꞌahine, Badiꞌaꞌa ḡaniroteꞌe ihoreḡa huga faine hegotoꞌi.
\p 
\v 15 Ḡa edeḡa, Asia habaꞌano ekalesia azaḡa niduꞌa eḡe muhihe iḡuniro. Zeḡe boꞌaḡano Fugelo ebu Heremogene zuni eḡe muhihe iḡuniro.
\v 16 E Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa Onesiforo ane neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa vetuḡazoga veize kurauꞌohe. Mazaḡa aniꞌa ḡae ḡehaḡa inarahiro ebu e ḡuꞌa neḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe moneo ani mene mazagaroniro.
\v 17 Ani Roma arirotene, ragave eḡe vaḡihi rae ufeta inaradu ḡiahiro.
\v 18 E Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa bariteꞌe madaḡano Onesiforo vetuḡanoga veize kurauꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe aniꞌa Efeso zamaḡano e ufeta danahirotaꞌaꞌe hube hune edereꞌohe.
\c 2
\s1 Keriso Iesu veize Gaueꞌeteꞌe Utiḡa Vazeḡa Manoḡa
\p 
\v 1 Timoteo, eḡe ubude, Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu aniꞌa ḡae mazao fureneꞌeteꞌe manoḡaḡa zamaḡano inaroꞌi.
\v 2 Eḡe ihore ḡoeꞌa igiroteꞌe azaḡa ḡehaḡa mazaonoꞌo ḡae zuni eḡe ihore ḡoeꞌa igiro. Ḡaeꞌa igiroteꞌe ihoreḡa ḡoeꞌa eꞌe iniu zamaze niduꞌa hina gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao ihozoꞌi, ꞌougine zeḡe zuni vaze ꞌahogaꞌahoga ihozogaꞌe idaraꞌuma.
\v 3 Ḡaꞌe Keriso Iesu veize utiteꞌeteꞌe uti vazeḡa manoḡa radu emeḡe teite ḡae zuni aduga moꞌi.
\v 4 Uti gauḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa gau nunu veize mada mene hauḡeꞌohe, mazaḡa aniꞌe uti vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa matuꞌohanoga veize uti gauḡa faine haḡaoga urateꞌohe.
\v 5 Iniu araho goroḡa mene hegote haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe naeḡa manoḡa mene hideꞌohe.
\v 6 Hihi azaḡa inare gaueꞌeteꞌeꞌa hiriviroteꞌe ogomuḡa ibite hidiꞌuma.
\v 7 Eḡeꞌa raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌahi faine zamaroꞌi, mazaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ḡaꞌe ḡoere eꞌe huga niduꞌa faine ederifine danaꞌiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 8 Eḡeꞌa haramiroteꞌe hariḡa manoḡa idunaḡano, Davida mariga zu rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare iḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa, Iesu Keriso zamaroꞌi.
\v 9 Eḡeꞌa hari manoḡa haramiroteꞌe uꞌano, e ḡonore vazeḡa teige ḡuꞌa neḡano mae ohohadu aduga hideꞌohe. Rehano Badiꞌa ḡoereꞌe ḡuꞌa neḡano ꞌuogaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\v 10 Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa veize e ḡau niduꞌa moneo zamahe obone giganeꞌohe. ꞌOugadu zeḡe zuni Keriso Iesu mazao fiadu ḡabone hidiꞌuma ebu ane teite ḡihiꞌa hune rae raꞌenaꞌa, radiu tuḡutuḡiꞌuma.
\v 11 Ḡoere ꞌahiꞌe huga:
\q1 Emeꞌa Keriso teite rudaro reine,
\q2 ani teite ḡabodiꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 12 Emeꞌa aduga niduꞌa zamaḡano zamafe obone giganine,
\q2 ani teite zuhiꞌaziꞌuma.
\q1 Emeꞌa ani oꞌonine,
\q2 ani zuni eme oꞌofiꞌuma.
\q1 
\v 13 Emeꞌa ani mazao mene fine zuni,
\q2 aniꞌa zamaḡa niduꞌa hina haḡae onamiꞌuma,
\q2 mazaḡa aniꞌe iḡaiḡa duduḡa radu ane ḡoitore ḡoeꞌa oꞌonogaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa mae Ḡihineꞌeteꞌe Gau Vazeḡa
\p 
\v 14 Eꞌa ḡaꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌadi ekalesia azaḡa bare ihozoꞌi. Ḡoere uꞌano mene rotetoga veize Badiꞌa ubumao riḡa iraduguzoꞌi. Rotetoꞌe huga oꞌoꞌa, ebu eꞌe igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ruizeꞌohe.
\v 15 Ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere huga duduḡano ihozoꞌi zu ḡauni ꞌahoga moneo ago mazagaroꞌoꞌi. Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe gau vazeḡano rouga veize zamaḡo niduꞌa hina inaroꞌi.
\v 16 Badiꞌa mene gubaneꞌenaꞌa, huga oꞌoꞌa ḡoeꞌa ḡoereꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi, mazaḡa ze ḡoere ꞌuguḡa raꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa mene ufeta gubaniꞌuma.
\v 17 Zeḡe ihoreꞌe borevo ugiḡa teige ḡarihe bororanadu vaze sausauziꞌuma. Zeḡe boꞌaḡano Humenaio ebu Fileto zuni ꞌouge ihozeꞌohe.
\v 18 Anianine ihore huga modadu Badiꞌaꞌa eme runeonoꞌo amahi bare ḡabofiro rae ihozeꞌohe zu vaze nuꞌa fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe zeḡeꞌa ꞌueꞌohe.
\v 19 Rehano Badiꞌa ḡoere hugaꞌe ne gadoḡa riḡa teige edau gigaruꞌohe, ebu eꞌe rana ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌe ane vaze edeḡa,”\x + \xo 2:19 \xt Naba 16:5 \x* zu “Iniu Zuhiꞌa Boro hegoteꞌohe rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuriꞌuma.”\x + \xo 2:19 \xt Naba 16:26 \x*
\p 
\v 20 Ne boro manoḡanoꞌe mene golo siuvaḡa zu siliva siuvaḡa daꞌo, rehano ire siuvaḡa zu raha siuvaḡa zuni eꞌe. Golo siuvaḡa zu siliva siuvaḡaꞌe mada boroboro veize maꞌohe, ebu ire siuvaḡa zu raha siuvaḡaꞌe mada niduꞌa veize maꞌohe.
\v 21 Iniuꞌa sauꞌa modadu ane bare dehenine, siuva manomano teige, ne vazeḡaniꞌa ani avo teadu gau manoḡa nunu haḡaifine ruhibiꞌuma, ebu aniꞌe ne vazeḡa veize gau vazeḡa manoḡa reꞌuma.
\p 
\v 22 Ḡaꞌe tahiꞌa iziganiꞌa haḡaihi raꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa sauꞌanonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi. Ebu zama deheḡa hina Zuhiꞌa Boro mazao umideꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teite, Badiꞌa ubumao haḡai duduḡa haḡaoga, Keriso mazao fioga, vaze zamaroga zu zama roḡeḡa veize inaroꞌi.
\v 23 Kauriḡa zu huga oꞌoꞌa taꞌiroḡano ago ꞌauḡoꞌi, mazaḡa ḡa edeḡa, eꞌe uꞌano rotetoꞌa fureruꞌohe.
\v 24 Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe vaze teite mene rotetiꞌuma, vaze niduꞌa mazao manoḡa haḡaiꞌuma, faine ihoziꞌuma, zu aduganonoꞌo zamaḡa obone tiꞌuma,
\v 25 ebu ani hezahohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni zama manoḡa hina ihoziꞌuma. ꞌOugine, Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe zamao gauadu zeꞌe haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuriꞌuma ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ibitozeadu ḡoere huga ederiꞌuma.
\v 26 Diaboloꞌa zeꞌe ꞌahirizeadu ze aniꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe gauḡa haḡaifine ibitoziro, rehano Badiꞌaꞌa danazadu ze zamare bariꞌuma ebu Diabolo mazaonoꞌo feraꞌuma. \fig Siuva nunu|src="WA04014b.tif" size="col" ref="2:20-26"\fig*
\c 3
\s1 Mada Ḡonagano Fureratiteꞌe Haḡaiḡa Sauꞌasauꞌa
\p 
\v 1 Ḡa ꞌahi ederoꞌi. Mada ḡonagano aduga madaḡa hidiꞌuma.
\v 2 Vazeꞌa zeḡe daꞌo zamare borofiꞌuma, ze hadi ubumaḡa reꞌuma, zeḡeꞌa bare niguziꞌuma, nize mae itiꞌuma, vaze rae sausauziꞌuma, nanu mama ḡoere mene igiꞌuma, manoḡa tauḡi rae mene reꞌuma, mene zaḡozaḡe radiꞌuma,
\v 3 vaze mene vetuḡaziꞌuma, vaze haḡai sauꞌa mene rae modiꞌuma, vaze rae sausauziꞌuma, zeḡeꞌa bare haḡai sauꞌa mene hezahohaꞌuma, uti fuꞌa reꞌuma, haḡai manoḡa heꞌeheꞌeniꞌuma,
\v 4 vaze revoziniꞌuma, mene faine zamaradu ḡurizabuo haḡaiꞌuma, ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡihiꞌa hune rae reꞌuma, Badiꞌa mene zamare borofadu zeḡe matuꞌu daꞌo zamare borofiꞌuma,
\v 5 ebu Badiꞌa ḡurire gubaniꞌuma, zu ḡaboneze ḡihuneꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa inaraḡaꞌe hezahohaꞌuma. Ḡa vaze ꞌuguḡa mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi.
\p 
\v 6 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano nuꞌe vaze ne sifu diuḡadu zamarone kauriḡa roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡa zamaze auꞌohe. Roḡae ꞌuguḡaꞌe haḡaize sauꞌa uꞌano aduga odoheꞌohe zu haḡai sauꞌa nunu haḡaihi rae zamareꞌohe.
\v 7 Zeꞌe iḡaiḡa edeḡa maꞌohe, rehano huga ederogaꞌe mene hune idaḡa.
\v 8 Iane zu Iamubareꞌa Mose agiroharoteꞌe teige, ḡuriro ihore azaḡaꞌe ihore huga agirohauꞌohe. Zeꞌe sauꞌa daꞌo zamareꞌohe zu ihore huga mene mae ḡihinadu Badiꞌaꞌa hezahoziniꞌohe.
\v 9 Rehano zeḡe haḡaiꞌe mene faḡa radiu onaꞌuma, mazaḡa vaze aheu eꞌe mazao naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe teige, zeꞌe kauriḡa rae vaze niduꞌa deheru ederiꞌuma.
\s1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa Ḡonaga
\p 
\v 10 Ḡaꞌe eḡe moneo niduꞌa edereꞌohe. Eḡe ihore ḡoeꞌa, eḡe haḡai, e nagini veize gaueꞌeteꞌe, e Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe, zamahe obone giganeꞌeteꞌe, vaze zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe zu aduganonoꞌo edau gigaruꞌeteꞌe,
\v 11 vazeꞌa e sausauhiroteꞌe, ebu eꞌa aduga boro hidirotaꞌaꞌe ḡa edeḡa. Antioka, Ikonio zu Lusitera habaꞌano naginiꞌa eḡe mazao fureraroteꞌe ebu eꞌa aduga eꞌe zamaḡano zamahe obone tirotaꞌaꞌe zuni ḡa edeḡa. Rehano Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa aduga eꞌe niduꞌaonoꞌo ḡabohiro.
\v 12 Hube hune, iniu Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu Badiꞌa gubaneꞌenaꞌa radihi rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe aduga hidiꞌuma.
\v 13 U sauꞌa azaḡa zu soꞌosoꞌo azaḡaꞌe soꞌosoꞌotitadu sauꞌazeꞌa ufeta bororaꞌuma.
\v 14 Rehano ḡa ḡaeꞌa ederiroteꞌe ebu hube hune mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa huga ꞌaune hegotoꞌi, mazaḡa ḡa iniuꞌa ihoꞌirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.
\v 15 Ebu ḡaꞌe tahiꞌa madaḡanonoꞌo Buka Zaḡoḡa ederiro. Ebu Buka Zaḡoḡaniꞌa zamarone huhuzaḡa ḡaniro ꞌahine, ḡaꞌe Keriso Iesu mazao fiadu ḡabone hideꞌeteꞌe moneo edere huneꞌohe.
\v 16 Buka Zaḡoḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa vaze zamao gauadu zeḡeꞌa mirihiro. Eꞌanoꞌo aꞌe vaze ihozoga, rozoga, duduzoga zu Badiꞌa ubumao haḡai duduḡa ihozoga veizeꞌe manoḡa.
\v 17 Eꞌanoꞌo Buka Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ihozadu Badiꞌa mone vazeḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa gau haḡaogaꞌe idaraꞌuma zu gau manoḡa niduꞌa faifaine haḡaiꞌuma.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Keriso Iesuꞌe ḡaboga azaḡa zu rune azaḡa kotaziteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌe bare aradu vaze niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌuma. E Badiꞌa zu Keriso Iesu ubumao riḡa ḡaꞌohe.
\v 2 Ḡa ḡoere huga haramoꞌi, zu manoḡa madaḡano ga sauꞌa madaḡano ꞌaune haramoga veize inaroꞌi. Zamaḡo riḡa obone giganeꞌenaꞌa zu faine ihozeꞌenaꞌa, vaze duduzoꞌi, zu rozoꞌi, ebu inarazoꞌi.
\v 3 Mazaḡa vazeꞌa ihore duduḡa mene igiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma. Eꞌe madaḡano ze zeḡe urao haḡai sauꞌa haḡaifine, zeḡeꞌa egogaꞌe iniga rae raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa daꞌo ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ḡeharu nuꞌoziꞌuma.
\v 4 Zeꞌe ḡoere huga mene igiꞌuma ebu irihine hegotiꞌuma.
\v 5 Rehano ḡaꞌe naginiꞌa fureruꞌeteꞌe faine ḡianeꞌenaꞌa haḡaoꞌi, aduga madaḡano zamaḡo obone giganoꞌi, Iesu hari manoḡa haramoꞌi, ebu Iesuꞌa ḡaniroteꞌe gauḡa niduꞌa haḡae hauḡoꞌi.
\p 
\v 6 Vaini vuḡa beꞌunadu dibuꞌeꞌeteꞌe\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Naba 15:5, 7, 10, 28:7. Aꞌe Badiꞌa mazao dibuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa ꞌahoga. Vaini vuḡaꞌe dibuꞌo fataḡano beꞌuneꞌenaꞌa, dibuꞌoharo. \f* teige, e amahi ruhe beꞌuniro ebu eḡeꞌa muhiziteꞌe madaḡaꞌe haniteha.
\v 7 E hari manoḡa veize faine utitiro, zu gauhe niduꞌa ibiḡano dure oname butiro, ebu eḡeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe obone giganiro.
\v 8 Eꞌanoꞌo e Badiꞌa ura ibiḡano duduḡa haḡadu Badiꞌaꞌa kini vadiga adiriḡa heuḡa naeḡa manoḡa eḡe veize ruhibiro. Eꞌe naeḡaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro, kota vazeḡa duduḡaniꞌa aneꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡano iniꞌuma. Aꞌe mene eḡe daꞌo, rehano iniu aniꞌa bare ariteꞌe guhine huneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ziniꞌuma.
\s1 Pauloꞌa Ane veize Timoteo Uminiro
\p 
\v 9 Ḡa eḡe vaḡe ḡarihe aroga inaroꞌi,
\v 10 mazaḡa Demaꞌa raha ꞌahi ufeta zamaradu muhihiro ebu Tesalonika onamiro. Kiresikeꞌe Galatia habaꞌa onamiro, u Titoꞌe Dalamatia habaꞌa onamiro.
\v 11 Luka daꞌo eḡe teite radiuꞌohe. Mareko zamahanadu ḡae teite aroꞌi, mazaḡa aniꞌe eḡe gauo danaheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.
\v 12 Eḡeꞌa Tukikoꞌe Efeso tuḡuniro.
\v 13 Ḡa aroꞌidene, Toroa zamaḡano eḡeꞌa Kapo mazao modiroteꞌe dabuaḡa baruḡa odohe aroꞌi. Zu eḡe buka odohe aroꞌi, ebu mani ogaḡa ranao mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡa nuꞌe hube hune odohe aroꞌi.
\p 
\v 14 Auri hina ḡau haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Alesanaꞌa eḡe mazao sauꞌa ḡehaḡa haḡairo. Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ane haḡai naeḡa haꞌuma.
\v 15 Ḡa zuni ani ḡianoꞌi, mazaḡa aniꞌa eme haramo riḡa agiroharo.
\p 
\v 16 E kotao eḡe veize ḡadahe birirotene, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zuni mene danahiro, rehano niduꞌa muhihiro. Rehano e Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe haḡai sauꞌa rae modoga veize kurauꞌohe.
\v 17 Rehano eḡeꞌa hari manoḡa niduꞌa harame hunifine zu Iuda mene azaḡa niduꞌa eꞌe igifine, Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa eḡe babaḡano edanadu inarahiro. Ebu laioni hebeonoꞌo e mae vaḡihiro.
\v 18 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa sauꞌa niduꞌaonoꞌo ḡabohiꞌuma ebu aneꞌa zuhiꞌaniꞌeteꞌe adureḡa habaꞌano faifaine tutuhe onamiꞌuma. Ani ni mae ḡihinihi, onamo tuḡutuḡu. Amen.
\s1 Uhiu Ḡoeꞌa
\p 
\v 19 Pirisika zu Akila, ebu Onesiforo zu ane neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao eḡe uhiu ḡoeꞌa zoꞌi.
\v 20 Erasitoꞌe Korinto zamaḡano radiuꞌohe, ebu Torofimoꞌe uginadu Mileto zamaḡano muhiniro.
\v 21 Nahune madaḡa ꞌizema mougano, ḡa ḡarihe ꞌahao feuroga inaroꞌi. Eubulu, Pude, Linu, Kulaudia, zu nego nabudi niduꞌa ḡae mazao uhiu ḡoeꞌa tuḡureꞌohe.
\p 
\v 22 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ḡae teite radiuꞌenoꞌi, ebu zae mazao manoḡa fureneꞌenoꞌi. 
